addAssociation(address,string).details: _name must not be empty and the address must not have been previously added as organization

params._address: The address to add as organization

addPet(string,string[],string,uint256).details: This pet will be linked to the association's address that originally called the function

params._needed: How much Ether this pet will need to pay for their recovery, expressed in Ether
params._photos: An array of photo pointers, a pointer is a hash that refer to a file stored in IPFS

params._hash: The hash pointing to an IPFS file

donate(uint256).details: The value sent to this function will increase the balances for the organization in charge

params._petId: The id of the pet to which we would like to donate

getPetsPage(uint256).details: The pages are calculated in reverse order of the way they were added to the contract

params.page: The page for which we would like to get the pets

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * > Note: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._isActive: Whether this pet is still under the organization's care or not

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._bio: The new bio of this pet
params._petId: The id of the pet whose bio is about to be changed

params._name: The new name of this pet
params._petId: The id of the pet whose name is about to be changed

devdoc.title: A contract to gather funds for Pets associations in developing countries.

addAssociation(address,string).notice: Adds a new organization to the contract, addresses added as organizations will be allowed to submit pets and withdraw money.

addPet(string,string[],string,uint256).notice: Adds a new pet to the contract

addPetPhoto(uint256,string).notice: Allows an organization to add a photo for a pet

donate(uint256).notice: Payable function that receives money for a given pet

getPageNumber().notice: Returns the number of pages that can be queried effectively

getPetsPage(uint256).notice: Retrieves the pets that belong to a given page, pagination is 1-based

setPetActive(uint256,bool).notice: Allows an organization to update whether this pet is still under their care or not

toggleCircuitBreaker().notice: Toggles the circuit breaker to stop the contract from working in case of emergency

updatePetBio(uint256,string).notice: Allows an organization to update the pet's bio

updatePetName(uint256,string).notice: Allows an organization to update the pet's name

withdraw().notice: Allows organizations to withdraw their balance stored in the contract
